name: Sunset Residences
description: Sunset Residences is a luxurious residential complex nestled in the heart of coastal California. With breathtaking ocean views and state-of-the-art amenities, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication. The complex features spacious apartments, a rooftop infinity pool, a fully-equipped fitness center, and landscaped gardens. Its prime location provides easy access to beaches, shopping districts, and fine dining experiences.
